data.description: MOTIVATED SELLER! This fully furnished home is being sold in the sought-after Citrus Hills community. This charming home is now available for sale, offering a fantastic opportunity for those looking to settle down in a peaceful neighborhood. Situated on a quiet cul-de-sac, this property boasts a spacious layout with two bedrooms and two bathrooms, providing ample space for comfortable living. The additional den offers flexibility and can be utilized as a home office, playroom, or guest room - the possibilities are endless. As you enter, you'll be greeted by the warm ambiance of this former builders model home. The interior features tasteful finishes and an abundance of natural light throughout. The fully landscaped yard adds to the curb appeal, while the tile roof ensures durability and longevity. One of the highlights of this property is the decked backyard extension, great for entertaining guests or enjoying a relaxing evening outdoors. With two parking spaces available, convenience is at your fingertips. Living in the Citrus Hills community means access to endless amenities. Take advantage of the gated entry for added security and peace of mind. Additionally, public water and sewer services provide convenience and ease of maintenance. Don't miss out on this incredible opportunity to own a beautiful home in one of the most desirable neighborhoods. Whether you're a first-time buyer or looking to downsize, this property offers everything you need for comfortable living. Schedule your showing today and experience all that 1710 North Sky Glenn Path has to offer!
